1. *Redu* se svugde poštuje. (Respect is honored everywhere.)
2. On je primio *redu*. (He received an order.)
3. Ona je uspešno završila *redu*. (She successfully completed the order.)
4. Mi smo sledili *redu*. (We followed the order.)
5. On je primio *redu* da ne radi. (He received an order not to work.)
6. Oni su joj dali *redu*. (They gave her an order.)
7. Ona je dobila *redu* da se vrati kući. (She was given an order to return home.)
8. On je naredio da se *redu* drži. (He ordered to keep the order.)
9. On je *redu* poštovao. (He respected the order.)
10. Ona je bila u mogućnosti da izvrši *redu*. (She was able to execute the order.)